    "description": "<strong>Dual Chroma: Academy Carols</strong> is a short prequel to our upcoming game: Dual Chroma, a fantasy romance visual novel. Select your magic type, pronouns and name and enter a magical world with other arcane students!<br><br>Story:<br>Winter break has come to Aradal. Unable to afford the journey back home, you brace yourself for a long snowfall alone at the Magic Academy, only to find you aren't the last student left on campus. What's more, among your newfound festive companions is the popular and typically unapproachable Prince Keldrannon - the last person you'd expect to stay.<br><br>What begins as a sad and solitary wintertide soon thaws into the promise of something far more precious. Warmth, friendship, perhaps even love.<br><br>A thoroughly merry and magical celebration may await you, after all.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>English Visual Novel<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Fully illustrated</li></ul>",
